description: On June 25, 1983, the Lord's Cricket Ground witnessed 14 men beat the two times World Champions West Indies, putting India back onto the cricket world stage.

title: Bhool Bhulaiyaa 2
description: When strangers Reet and Ruhan cross paths, their journey leads to an abandoned mansion and a dreaded spirit who has been trapped for 18 years.

title: Runway 34
description: Inspired by true incidents, 'Runway 34' revolves around Captain Vikrant Khanna played by Ajay Devgn, a flying prodigy, whose flight takes a mysterious course after take-off from an international destination.

title: Gangubai Kathiawadi
description: Duped and sold to a brothel, a young woman fearlessly reclaims her power, using underworld connections to preside over the world she was once a pawn in.

title: Sooryavanshi
description: Sooryavanshi traces the acts and serious antics of DCP Veer Sooryavanshi, the chief of the Anti-Terrorism Squad in India.

title: Ra.One
description: When the titular antagonist of an action game takes on physical form, it's only the game's less powerful protagonist who can save his creator's family.

title: Jersey
description: A cricketer who quits cricket decides to revive his career at the age of 36 for his sons dream and prove his ability.

title: Kal Ho Naa Ho
description: Naina, an introverted, perpetually depressed girl's life changes when she meets Aman. But Aman has a secret of his own which changes their lives forever. Embroiled in all this is Rohit, Naina's best friend who conceals his love for her.
